 01. Lana Del Rey vs Cedric Gervais - Young & Beautiful (Remix) [7:01]


 
                  Cedric Gervais did it again!
 He remixed the wonderful "Young & Beautiful" (title track to Hollywood masterpiece The Great Gadsby) just like he did with Lana del Rey's previous hit "Summertime Sadness" - which dominated the Beatport chart for weeks.
 This time around he created a huge progressive production centered around those heavenly Lana del Rey vocals. This will go to the top of the charts once again, no doubt! BOMB!
